Implementation Notes

1. Redundancy: All critical systems (Zone 1, Zone 4 grid connection) utilize N+1 redundancy.
2. Standards Compliance: IEEE 802.11ax (WiFi 6E/7) for wireless; ISO 50001 for Energy Management.
3. Future-Proofing: Conduit capacity at 40% initial fill rate to accommodate future photonic cabling and sensor technologies.
